column5: I dunno Norm, but I couldn't get this to open in the email you sent me and I can't get this one to open either  Very strange indeed.
Works for me here Lew...maybe clear your cache and reboot ???
Did all that Norm and still nothing.  Oh well....
That was very cool.   Thanks for sharing.
Cute  I was waiting for something funny to happen... Oh well...
Thanks Brian  Excellent video Norm, well worth waiting for !!  Not much better than a boy and his pooch loving each other !!
Very cute.. Reminds me of my daughter and our long gone Dalmation..Molly!
There is a testament to labs!

Thanks for posting that Norm! Quite an example of unconditional love on both their parts. That is one very good natured Lab! Not a young dog either, but very patient. I don't think I would have let the boy climb on him like that, but hey, he does not seem to mind!
